{
  "page": "Roderick Stark",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> <b>Brandon Stark</b>, known as Brandon the Boisterous, and <b>Roderick Stark</b> are not mentioned in any of <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a>'s published work. Instead they became known to the fandom via a comment from <a href=\"/index.php/User:Ran\" title=\"User:Ran\">Elio \"Ran\" García</a>, co-author of <i>The World of Ice &amp; Fire</i>, based on the notes Martin shared to him regarding the lineage of House Stark.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Lineage_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Lineage-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Not to be confused with <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Stark\" title=\"Rodrik Stark\">Rodrik Stark</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/50px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/75px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/100px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Roderick Stark</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/50px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/75px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/100px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Lord of Winterfell\">Lord of Winterfell</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_North\" title=\"Warden of the North\">Warden of the North</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">Northmen</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Roderick Stark</b> was the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a> during the first half of the first century after <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Roderick_Stark&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Roderick was succeeded as <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Lord of Winterfell\">Lord of Winterfell</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_North\" title=\"Warden of the North\">Warden of the North</a> by <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark_(father_of_Walton)\" title=\"Brandon Stark (father of Walton)\">Brandon Stark</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Lineage_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Lineage-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Roderick_Stark&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>His relation to his successor Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark_(father_of_Walton)\" title=\"Brandon Stark (father of Walton)\">Brandon Stark</a> is unknown.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Lineage_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Lineage-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\